# Phishing-Case-Study


## Email Sample Analyzed

> **From:** Doug Williams <chrispid@t-online.de>
> **Date:** Wed, Apr 13, 2020 at 11:47 AM
> **Subject:** Invoice for Lehigh University; Attention: Controller
> **To:** j
